Let \(R\) be a ring and suppose that we have the following commutative diagram of \(R\)-modules and module homomorphisms with exact rows.
\[
\require{amscd}
\begin{CD}
0 @>>> A @>{f}>> B @>{g}>> C @>>> 0 \\
@. @V{\alpha}VV @V{\beta}VV @V{\gamma}VV @. \\
0 @>>> A' @>{f'}>> B' @>{g'}>> C' @>>> 0
\end{CD}
\]
